{"tid":2197311,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]GUNDAM BATTLE OPERATION 2 [89] 新機好鬼勁！","createTime":"2020-09-10T13:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T17:16:52.000Z","uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35c7945e47d54218f74508261495b6ab97bd9bf5","tid":2197311,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T13:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2w7dKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2w7dKh.jpg&h=440a6bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於近期軍團戰人數不足<br />\n為方便各位巴打參戰，依家會跟據軍團戰參加意向分軍團<br />\n而新入團都請填表<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ivpW-JmDfQvJexG0DVCQ-HWCVEaSoFL1cSjw1Ns_Qmw/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1ivpW-JmDfQvJexG0DVCQ-HWCVEaSoFL1cSjw1Ns_Qmw%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=c0006306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ivpW-JmDfQvJexG0DVCQ-HWCVEaSoFL1cSjw1Ns_Qmw/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n主團 lhk:時代革命軍<br />\n副團 li:下格新人類團<br />\n副團2 hea:LIHKGhea打歐洲人<br />\n<br />\n新手團 hk1: 願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\nhk1 入團表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/AwTTrcoB9ZavBXHU7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FAwTTrcoB9ZavBXHU7&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=d37550c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/AwTTrcoB9ZavBXHU7</a><br />\n<br />\n日文官網: <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=d819124d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp</a><br />\n中文官網 : <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp%2Fhk%2F&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=8d8a5614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/</a><br />\n遊戲Wiki: <a href=\"https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fbattle-operation2&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=9b3db5a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2</a><br />\n新手注意<br />\n溫馨提示:咩都唔識就搵𡃁妹玩下訓練先<br />\n順手拎部200cost神器訓練吉<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKEKMn0X1MHk&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=8906f777\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\nFAQ<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解我成日斷線<br />\nA. 為己為人, <del>自殺</del>對戰請用Lan 線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ. 今集有無EN限制?係咪好似上集兩個鐘先回1粒EN?<br />\nA. 今集廢除咗EN, 玩真人體力制, 燃燒自己嘅小宇宙啦<br />\n<br />\nQ. 有無分Server? 用港定日psn 好?<br />\nA. 今集係國際Server, 港日psn 都係一齊玩, 但之前GBON轉Server 前科, 所以用日psn應該會安全啲<br />\n<br />\nQ. 可唔可以同朋友一齊開房玩<br />\nA. Ranking 同Quick請用正方入房之後邀朋友, 自訂直接入房之後邀朋友<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣用支援炮擊<br />\nA. 佔點之後會見到有個數字倒數, 當倒數到0之後就可以落機call 炮擊, 威力極大如善用可以一擊逆轉戰況<br />\n<br />\nQ. 機/武/Parts 點樣升lv?<br />\nA. 用DP直接買下一lv, 如果未有得買即係未夠軍階<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣放炸彈<br />\nA. 1. 基礎戰先有得放<br />\n2. 去到基地搵 [ ! ]個ICON<br />\n3. 行到正確嘅位置,就會有話框叫你長按正方裝炸彈<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣出滾地 (緊急迴避)<br />\nA. 如果你部機有&rdquo;緊急迴避制御&ldquo; skill就可以連按兩次Boost掣使出急迴<br />\n(Default setting 即係連按X)<br />\n<br />\nQ:部機lv1用唔用到lv5武器？<br />\nA:無限場所有lv都得<br />\n限cost場要跟機lv, 高過部機過就降到你所持有嘅武器當中與機體同級或以下lv<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣出反格<br />\nA. 對方出格鬥時按三角撞埋去, 判定時機請自行練習<br />\n<br />\nQ. 格鬥點出二連斬三連斬<br />\nA. 機體要有&rdquo;格鬥連擊制御&ldquo; Skill, lv1可以2hit, lv2可以3hit<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解有人可以斬完又斬好似無硬直?<br />\nA. 運用Boost Cancel 技巧就可以解除攻擊後嘅硬直(包括火箭炮, 加農炮, 格鬥, etc), 方法係攻擊後立即輕按Boost step 走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手製SETTING建議<br />\n打之前改改手製個SETTING<br />\nDefault 用X加速搞到加速其間好難轉方向<br />\nR1轉武R2射又令人好易轉錯武<br />\n所以改成<br />\nR1射<br />\nR2轉武<br />\nL1加速<br />\nX跳<br />\n其他不變<br />\n<br />\nCredit: 浴缸裡的貓, <a href=\"http://One.For.All\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOne.For.All&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=09b455a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://One.For.All</a>, 高熱火焰, 闇之大精靈<br />\n<br />\n怎麼才算好泛機隊友? #曲<br />\n1.) 開場時散開衝, 唔好係我前面阻住我衝<br />\n2.) 到主戰場企係我前面擋彈, 等我定好位先好走<br />\n3.) 我射時唔該有後眼自動遠離我射線<br />\n4.) 我比人射時唔該有NT感應BOOST過黎幫我擋彈<br />\n5.) 擋完彈之後好馬上急回彈開等我可以零秒反擊<br />\n6.) 有格機打我你地要血肉長城保護我<br />\n7.) 就算因為保護我而死, 唔該死遠D免得爆炸D光影響我, D煙唔該飄遠D唔好影響我開鏡<br />\n<br />\n屌你班歐洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uKwdvWE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuKwdvWE.gif&h=34225e98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8feba9cf65ee0105581e3ce3976285e860b95aa0","tid":2197311,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T13:41:32.000Z","msg":"大家sorry 我開錯post 請去番絕影OuO 嘅post 到討論"},{"pid":"93c4c336ee4bacb34072df106c71f6bb35f41fc9","tid":2197311,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:14:03.000Z","msg":"封面慢咗2星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c053f6a1e6df168eae6aad544ebd49b726c133ba","tid":2197311,"uid":119069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:14:33.000Z","msg":"Mk2係咪好嘢?<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGpSwzj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGpSwzj.png&h=69e7bea2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb3c7bb21fd93fdd529bf30c8484b5a3dc45fa8c","tid":2197311,"uid":119069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqUWdOg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqUWdOg.png&h=60239071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩又中多部三星<br />\n呢部勁唔勁?"}]}